<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Halliburton upped to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Halliburton upped to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers said it upgraded Halliburton Co to buy from hold.</p>
<p>-- Cited stronger earnings outlook, improved prospects for pricing increases that would boost earnings further and attractive valuation based on current estimates.</p>
<p>-- Said raised the 1997 earnings estimate to $3.30 a share from $3.00 a share and raised the 1998 earnings estimate to $3.95 a share from $3.65 a share.</p>
<p>-- Shares gained 4-7/8 to 73-3/4.</p>
<p>(( -- Wall Street desk 212-859-1730))</p>
